dockerz (2.0.0-1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Major version bump to 2.0 with complete rewrite in Go.
  * Added smart build features: git change detection, multi-level caching, and smart orchestration.
  * Added automatic image name normalization to Docker-compatible kebab-case.
  * Added CI/CD integration with --changed-services-file and --output-changed-services flags.
  * Added new CLI flags: --smart, --git-track, --cache, --force, --project-id, --region, --gar-name, --tag, --changed-services-file, --output-changed-services.
  * Enhanced configuration with smart features support.
  * Improved build performance with intelligent service filtering.
  * Migrated from Python to Go for better performance and maintainability.

